<!-- ============================================================
     ABOUT / MANIFESTO SECTION
============================================================ -->
<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div class="about-left reveal-left">
        <div class="about-accent-line"></div>
        <span class="eyebrow">WHO WE ARE</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">
          We Don't Just Install Solar—<br>
          <em>We Engineer the Future.</em>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column -->
      <div class="about-right reveal">
        <p class="body-text">Solara was founded on a singular belief: Pakistan deserves world-class solar infrastructure. With over 15 years of experience and 720+ successful installations, we've built a reputation for uncompromising quality, precision engineering, and long-term partnerships with our clients.</p>
        <p class="body-text">From residential rooftops in DHA Lahore to multi-megawatt industrial installations in Karachi, every project we undertake is engineered with the same obsessive attention to detail. We don't cut corners — we engineer solutions that outlast warranties and outperform projections.</p>
        <p class="body-text">Our team of certified solar engineers, electrical specialists, and project managers brings global expertise to Pakistan's unique energy landscape — designing systems that account for local sun hours, grid conditions, and climate patterns.</p>

        <div class="about-values">
          <span>INNOVATION</span>
          <span class="value-dash">—</span>
          <span>PRECISION</span>
          <span class="value-dash">—</span>
          <span>SUSTAINABILITY</span>
        </div>

        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="/images/about-team.jpg" alt="Solara engineers on a solar installation" loading="lazy"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

